In the last sentence, Andrej is revealing that he has already downloaded the Tiny Shakespeare dataset that they will use to train the Transformer-based language model. He has opened this file which is around one megabyte in size. With this dataset, Andrej will showcase and explain how a transformer is trained to understand and generate text that follows the pattern of Shakespeare's writing style. He highlights that the file contains all the works of Shakespeare, proving it to be a comprehensive tool for the intended tutorial.